    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-1a' );" name="002-1a" class="pb">[002-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　周易舉正卷中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:218'>　　　　　　　　　　　　唐　郭京　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='218:241'>咸彖註不能感非類也謹按不字誤作亦字感非類冬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='241:255'>　筍之應候註疏比類况詳之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='255:278'>遯彖小利貞浸而長註隂道雖浸而長正道亦未全滅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='278:301'>　故小利貞也謹按雖字誤作欲字子欲居九夷召子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='301:324'>　欲往皆未往之辭卦有六爻兩爻已變不可言欲誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='324:350'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-1b' );" name="002-1b" class="pb">[002-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='350:356'>　亦明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='356:379'>大壯六五喪牛于易註牛壯也而喪其牛失其所居者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='379:402'>　也能喪壯于易不於險難故得无悔二履正吉能幹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='402:425'>　其任而已委焉則得无悔委之則難不至居之則敵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='425:448'>　冦来故曰喪牛于易象曰喪牛于易經註象五牛字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='448:468'>　並誤作羊字大壯之義莫先於牛義可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='468:491'>明夷上六至晦註處明夷之極是至晦者也謹按晦字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='491:514'>　上脫至字誤增不明字按初九註明夷之主在於上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='514:540'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-2a' );" name="002-2a" class="pb">[002-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='540:563'>　六上六為至暗者也據此三爻註義至晦之理極明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='563:570'>　斷可知矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='570:593'>蹇象曰山上有水蹇君子以正身修徳註除難莫若正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='593:616'>　身修徳也謹按經註正字並誤作反字且博聞强識</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='616:639'>　而譲敦善行而不怠謂之君子既成君子之名若反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='639:662'>　君子之身則是小人之道又曰難由正濟又曰遇難</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='662:685'>　失正吉可得乎足明反身之義乖矣亦固在不惑昭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='685:691'>　然顯著</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='691:717'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-2b' );" name="002-2b" class="pb">[002-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='717:740'>六二王臣蹇蹇匪躬之故註履中行義以存其正也謹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='740:763'>　按正字誤作上字疏云六二是五之臣往應于五履</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='763:786'>　正居中志匡王家能涉蹇難而往濟蹇疏意祇為六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='786:806'>　二履正居中能濟蹇難觀疏尋義誤亦可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='806:829'>九三往蹇来正註進則入險来則得位故曰往蹇来正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='829:851'>　為下卦之主是内之所恃也象曰往蹇来正謹按</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='851:874'>　經註象三正字並誤作反字此爻辭註爻皆當位各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='874:897'>　履其正又六四註得位履正當其本實九五註居不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='897:923'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-3a' );" name="002-3a" class="pb">[002-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='923:942'>　失正據四節正字義足明三處反字誤也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='942:965'>解初六无咎註解者解散也屯難盤結於是乎解也謹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='965:980'>　按脫散字已於上經剥卦論訖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='980:1003'>損六五或益之十朋之龜弗克違元吉註隂非先唱柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1003:1026'>　非自任尊以自居損以守之故民用其力士竭其功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1026:1049'>　智者慮能明者慮策弗能違也則衆才之用盡矣謹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1049:1072'>　按士字誤作事字按註疏初論庶民次舉衆士三用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1072:1095'>　才智四任明逺則是衆才之義非闗物務諸事蓋為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1095:1121'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-3b' );" name="002-3b" class="pb">[002-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1121:1133'>　士事聲相近因而誤焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1133:1156'>益六三益之用凶事无咎有孚中行告公用圭註以隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1156:1179'>　居陽求益者也故曰益之益不外來已自為之物所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1179:1202'>　不與也故在謙則戮救凶則免以隂居陽處下卦之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1202:1225'>　上壯之甚也用救衰危物所恃也故用凶事得无咎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1225:1248'>　也若能益不為私志在救難壯不至亢信不失中以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1248:1271'>　此告公國主所任也用圭之禮備此道矣故曰有孚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1271:1294'>　中行告公用圭也公者臣之極也凡事足以施天下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1294:1320'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-4a' );" name="002-4a" class="pb">[002-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1320:1343'>　則稱王次天下之大者則稱公六三才不足以告王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1343:1366'>　足以告公而得用圭者故曰告公用圭也謹按亢字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1366:1389'>　下脫信字中字下誤增行字其信字本為有孚生義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1389:1402'>　審詳首末註義義亦自明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1402:1425'>姤女壯勿用取女彖曰姤遇也柔遇剛也女壯勿用取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1425:1448'>　女不可與長也謹按爻辭取字下誤增女字彖辭勿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1448:1471'>　用取上脫女壯字勿用取下誤增女字非但不背定</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1471:1495'>　本審詳六十四卦爻彖理例誤增誤脱亦甚昭晰可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1495:1521'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-4b' );" name="002-4b" class="pb">[002-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1521:1544'>初六繫于金柅貞吉有攸往見凶羸豕孚蹢躅註羸豕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1544:1567'>　牝豕也羣豕之中豭强而牝弱故謂之羸豕也孚猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1567:1590'>　鶩躁也夫隂質而躁怒羸豕特甚焉言以不貞之隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1590:1613'>　失其所牽其為淫醜若羸豕鶩蹢躅也謹按鶩字並</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1613:1632'>　作務字字義恰作鶩字觀察義理自明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1632:1655'>九二包有魚无咎不利賔註初隂而窮下故稱魚不正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1655:1678'>　之隂處遇之始不能逆近者也初自樂来應己之厨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1678:1701'>　非為犯奪故无咎擅人之物以為己惠義所不為故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1701:1727'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-5a' );" name="002-5a" class="pb">[002-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1727:1750'>　不利賔也九四包无魚起凶註二有其魚故失之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1750:1773'>　无民而動失應而作是以凶也謹按无字誤作失字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1773:1787'>　審詳九二爻註義義斯見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1787:1810'>九五似杞包瓜含章有隕自天註杞之為物生于肥地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1810:1833'>　包瓜為物繫而不食九五履得尊位不遇其應得地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1833:1856'>　而不食含章而未發不遇其應命未流行然處得其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1856:1879'>　所體剛居中志不舍命而不可傾隕故曰有隕自天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1879:1901'>　也謹按似字誤作以字審詳爻註文義義自見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1901:1927'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-5b' );" name="002-5b" class="pb">[002-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1927:1950'>萃亨王假有廟利見大人亨利貞用大牲吉利有攸往</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1950:1973'>　彖曰萃聚也順以說剛中而應故聚也王假有廟致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1973:1996'>　孝亨也利見大人亨利貞聚以正也用大牲吉利有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1996:2019'>　攸往順天命也謹按彖舉爻辭脫利貞字凡六十卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2019:2042'>　彖先舉爻辭後以義結皆无遺漏具録彖如前審而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2042:2051'>　詳之脫亦明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2051:2074'>六三萃如嗟如无攸利往无咎小吝註履非其位以比</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2074:2097'>　於四四亦失位不正不正相聚患所生也今本註履</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2097:2123'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-6a' );" name="002-6a" class="pb">[002-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2123:2146'>　非其位以比于四四亦失位不正相聚患所生也謹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2146:2169'>　按註失位不正字下更合有不正字相聚字下不合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2169:2192'>　更有相聚不正字具録定本今本如上審而詳之誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2192:2198'>　可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2198:2221'>困初六臀困于株木入于幽谷三歳不覿謹按彖曰入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2221:2243'>　于幽谷不明也不明字上誤增幽字義亦甚明也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2243:2266'>井改邑不改井无喪无得往来井井汔至亦未繘井羸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2266:2289'>　其瓶凶彖曰㢲乎水而上水井井養而不窮也改邑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2289:2315'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-6b' );" name="002-6b" class="pb">[002-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2315:2338'>　不改井无喪无得往来井井乃以剛中也汔至亦未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2338:2361'>　繘井未有功也羸其瓶是以凶也謹按脫无喪无得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2361:2385'>　往来井井兩句凡彖先舉卦名釋訖次舉爻辭後以義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2385:2402'>　結六十三卦无如此者足明誤脱矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2402:2425'>鼎元吉亨彖曰鼎象也以木㢲火亨飪也聖人亨以享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2425:2448'>　上帝以養聖賢註亨者鼎之所為也革去故而鼎取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2448:2471'>　新故為亨飪調和之器也去故取新聖賢不可失也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2471:2494'>　飪熟也天下莫不用也乃上以亨上帝而下以養聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2494:2520'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-7a' );" name="002-7a" class="pb">[002-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2520:2543'>　賢也謹按經帝字下誤增而大亨字註養字上誤增</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2543:2562'>　大亨字非但定本且義理冗長誤自明焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2562:2585'>震亨震来虩虩笑言啞啞震驚百里不喪匕鬯彖曰震</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2585:2608'>　亨震来虩虩恐致福也笑言啞啞後有則也震驚百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2608:2631'>　里驚逺而懼邇也不喪匕鬯出可以守宗廟社稷以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2631:2654'>　為祭主也註明所以堪長子之義也不喪匕鬯則已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2654:2677'>　出可以守宗廟社稷也謹按經脫不喪匕鬯字註脫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2677:2691'>　社稷字非唯定本理義且乖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2691:2717'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-7b' );" name="002-7b" class="pb">[002-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2717:2740'>艮其背不獲其身行其庭不見其人无咎註凡物對面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2740:2763'>　而不相通否之道也艮止也不相交通之卦各止而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2763:2786'>　不相與何得无咎唯不相見乃可也施止於背不見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2786:2809'>　其所欲而得其所止也背者无見之處也无見則自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2809:2832'>　然静止静止而无見則不獲其身矣相背者雖近而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2832:2855'>　不相見故行其庭不見其人也夫施止不於无見令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2855:2878'>　物自然而止若强止之則姦邪並興近而不相得則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2878:2901'>　凶其得无咎者艮其背而不獲其身行其庭不見其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2901:2927'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-8a' );" name="002-8a" class="pb">[002-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2927:2950'>　人故也謹按註見其所字誤作隔物字背者无見之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2950:2973'>　處處字誤作物字其得无咎下脫者字亦詳義可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2973:2977'>　矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2977:3000'>彖艮其止止其所也註艮背曰止以明背則止也施止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3000:3022'>　不可於面施背乃可也施止於止不施止於行得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3022:3045'>　其所也故曰艮其止止其所也謹按註首艮字今本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3045:3059'>　多作易字觀其義義可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3059:3082'>九三艮其限註止加其限謹按限字誤作身字但詳六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3082:3108'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-8b' );" name="002-8b" class="pb">[002-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3108:3120'>　四爻及註則義可知矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3120:3143'>六四艮其身无咎註中上稱身履得其位止於諸身得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3143:3166'>　其所處故不陷於咎也謹按於字誤作求字義亦可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3166:3171'>　知矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3171:3194'>漸彖女歸吉也謹按漸彖女歸吉下誤增也字已於上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3194:3202'>　經比卦論訖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3202:3225'>象君子以居賢徳善風俗賢徳以止㢲則居風俗以止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3225:3248'>　㢲則善謹按脫風字觀註可知文句圓暢若无風字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3248:3274'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-9a' );" name="002-9a" class="pb">[002-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3274:3285'>　則文闕理亦甚明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3285:3308'>歸妹六五小象不如其娣之袂良謹按良字下誤增也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3308:3331'>　字驗三百八十三爻小象先舉爻辭後以義結爻辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3331:3343'>　下盡无也字誤亦明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3343:3366'>豐初九遇其配主雖旬无咎往有尚註處豐之初其配</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3366:3389'>　在四以陽適陽以明之動能相光大者也旬均之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3389:3412'>　初四俱陽爻故曰均也是以雖旬无咎往有尚也今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3412:3435'>　本註處豐之初其配在四以陽適陽以明之動能相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3435:3461'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-9b' );" name="002-9b" class="pb">[002-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3461:3484'>　光大者也旬均也雖均无咎往有尚也初四俱陽爻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3484:3507'>　故曰均也謹按註初四俱陽爻故曰均也雖旬无咎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3507:3530'>　往有尚也前雖字上仍脫是以字雖字下旬字又誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3530:3553'>　作均字為脫誤相仍恐難分别故兩録定本今本對</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3553:3569'>　明在達者審而詳之是非可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3569:3592'>九四豐其蔀日中見斗遇其夷主吉象曰豐其蔀位不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3592:3615'>　當也日中見斗幽不明也遇其夷主吉志行也謹按</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3615:3638'>　脫志字小象皆先爻辭後以義結遇其夷主吉既是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3638:3665'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-10a' );" name="002-10a" class="pb">[002-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3665:3688'>　爻辭行之一字亦未成義謹按睽卦初四俱陽爻小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3688:3705'>　象云志行也比例詳義足見其脫矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3705:3728'>旅小亨旅貞吉彖曰旅小亨柔得中乎外而順乎剛止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3728:3751'>　而麗乎明是以小亨旅貞吉也註夫物失其主則散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3751:3774'>　柔乗於剛則乖既乖且散物皆羇旅何由得小亨而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3774:3797'>　貞吉也夫陽為物長而隂皆順陽惟六五乗剛而復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3797:3820'>　得中乎外以承於上隂皆順陽不為乖逆止而麗明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3820:3844'>　動不履妄雖不及剛得尊位恢𢎞大道是以小亨令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3844:3871'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-10b' );" name="002-10b" class="pb">[002-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3871:3894'>　羇旅者不失其正得所安也謹按羇字誤作附字審</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3894:3905'>　詳經註大義斯明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3905:3928'>初六旅瑣瑣㒋其所取災註最處下極寄旅不得所安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3928:3951'>　而為㒋賤之役所取致災志窮且困謹按㒋字並合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3951:3974'>　作㒋賤之義不合作斯此之意觀詳經註察其義理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3974:3984'>　亦甚分明可知矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3984:4007'>六五射雉一矢亡終以譽命註射雉以一矢而又亡之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4007:4030'>　則雖有雉而終不可得寄旅而進雖處文明之中居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4030:4057'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-11a' );" name="002-11a" class="pb">[002-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4057:4080'>　于貴位終不可有也以其能知禍福之萌不安其處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4080:4103'>　以棄其下而上承於上故終以譽而見命謹按棄字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4103:4127'>　誤作乗字未有𨽻書以前棄字與乗字相類轉寫漸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4127:4136'>　誤理亦可昭矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4136:4159'>㢲彖重㢲以申命命乃行也註未有不㢲而命行也謹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4159:4182'>　按命乃行也一句誤入註觀文尋義義亦相連了不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4182:4205'>　闗註至如大過彖註以此救難難乃濟也又與易窮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4205:4228'>　則變變則通通則久又與艮彖艮其止止其所也又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4228:4255'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-11b' );" name="002-11b" class="pb">[002-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4255:4278'>　與蹇爻註居難履正正邦之道何殊並義理相連誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4278:4284'>　亦明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4284:4307'>九五註以陽居陽損於謙㢲然秉乎中正以宣其令物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4307:4330'>　莫之違故曰貞吉悔亡无不利也謹按註然字下誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4330:4353'>　增後字其六四註乗剛則悔也然得位乗五卑得所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4353:4376'>　奉雖以柔御剛而位尊履正斯行命必能獲强暴逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4376:4399'>　不仁驗六四註然字義與九五然字義理一同誤增</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4399:4408'>　後字理亦明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4408:4435'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-12a' );" name="002-12a" class="pb">[002-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4435:4458'>渙亨王假有廟利涉大川利貞彖曰渙亨剛来而不窮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4458:4481'>　柔得位乎外而上同註二以剛来居内以不窮於險</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4481:4504'>　四以柔得位乎外而與上同内剛而无險困之難外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4504:4527'>　順而无違逆之乖是以亨利涉大川利貞也凡剛得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4527:4550'>　暢而无忌回之累柔履正而同志乎剛則皆亨利涉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4550:4573'>　大川利貞也王假有廟王乃在中也利涉大川利貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4573:4596'>　乗木有功也註乗木即涉難也木者所以涉川也涉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4596:4619'>　難而常用正道必有功也謹按利涉大川下脫利貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4619:4646'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-12b' );" name="002-12b" class="pb">[002-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4646:4669'>　字審詳爻辭及彖註足明脫矣又註木者所以涉川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4669:4692'>　也所以字下誤增専字専字訓獨不二之義木之為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4692:4715'>　用廣矣大矣而云専涉川豈不大乖乎又註涉難而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4715:4738'>　常用正道正字誤作渙字蹇爻註正道未否難由正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4738:4761'>　濟遇難失正吉可得乎此涉難與蹇難何殊足明合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4761:4778'>　用正道不合用渙離散之義亦明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4778:4801'>節亨苦節不可貞彖曰節亨剛柔分而剛得中苦節不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4801:4824'>　可貞其道窮也說以行險當位以節中正以通然後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4824:4851'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-13a' );" name="002-13a" class="pb">[002-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4851:4874'>　乃亨也註无說而行險過中而為節則道窮也謹按</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4874:4897'>　然後乃亨也一句誤將入註此一句元釋節卦有孚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4897:4920'>　通之義審詳六十四卦爻彖義例足見誤矣且序卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4920:4943'>　云有天地然後有萬物又孝經富貴不離其身然後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4943:4966'>　能保其社稷子曰吾自衛反於魯然後樂正雅頌各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4966:4989'>　得其所又曰嵗寒然後知松柏之後凋也且六經三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4989:5012'>　史及凡著述未有无發端而以然後為首辭者理亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5012:5017'>　明矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5017:5044'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-13b' );" name="002-13b" class="pb">[002-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5044:5067'>中孚豚魚吉信及也謹按及字下誤增豚魚字驗六十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5067:5090'>　四卦彖先舉爻辭後以義結更不重言爻文足明誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5090:5094'>　矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5094:5117'>九二鳴鶴在隂其子和之我有好爵吾與爾縻之註居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5117:5140'>　内而處重隂之下而履不失中不徇于外任真者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5140:5163'>　立誠篤信雖在暗昧物亦應焉故曰鳴鶴在隂其子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5163:5186'>　和之不私權利唯徳是與誠之至也故曰我有好爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5186:5209'>　吾與爾縻之言與物散之謹按脫吾與爾縻之并言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5209:5236'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-14a' );" name="002-14a" class="pb">[002-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5236:5254'>　字驗三百八十四爻註義例足明誤矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5254:5277'>小過亨利貞可小事不可大事飛鳥遺之音不宜上宜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5277:5300'>　下大吉彖小過小者過也過以利貞與時行也柔得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5300:5323'>　中是以可小事也謹按是以下脫可字小事下誤增</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5323:5346'>　吉字彖舉爻辭例无增損若可小事下合有吉則不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5346:5367'>　可大事下合有凶則小事不合有吉斷可知也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5367:5390'>六五小象密雲不雨已止也註陽已止下故也謹按經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5390:5413'>　註止字並誤作上字故字上仍脫下字察其文義可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5413:5440'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0010', 'WYG', '002-14b' );" name="002-14b" class="pb">[002-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5440:5445'>　見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5445:5448'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5448:5451'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5451:5454'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5454:5457'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5457:5460'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5460:5463'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5463:5472'>　周易舉正卷中</span><br/>
